\begin_inset Formula $F_{1},F_{2}$
\end_inset

的线性方程组，求解得到
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
 & F_{1}=\frac{-A\left(4m^{2}+Q^{2}\right)-2mB}{4\left(4m^{2}+Q^{2}\right)},\quad F_{2}=\frac{-mB}{2\left(4m^{2}+Q^{2}\right)}\\
